print(df)
Displays the complete dataset with the new Age_group column.
________________________________________
6. Group Data by Age Group
grouped=df.groupby('Age_group', observed=False)
Meaning:
Groups rows according to:
•	Young 
•	Middle 
•	Senior 
________________________________________
7. Calculate Summary Statistics
print(grouped['Income'].agg(['mean','median','min','max','std']))
This calculates statistics of Income for each age group.
________________________________________
Meaning of Each Function
Function	Meaning
mean	Average
